data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. SELLER IS OPEN TO OFFERING RATE BUY DOWN or CLOSING COSTS!! NEW ROOF-NEW AC - NEW Kitchen - NEW Interior Paint - NEW Massive Sliding Doors - NEW Pool Pump This very spacious home offers over 2000s SF with a traditional split-level floor plan with 3 large bedrooms, 2.5 baths, great room, oversized living room and dining area leading into a large, remodeled kitchen with new cabinets, granite counter tops, and appliances. The great room which can be used as a media room, family room, has expansive sliding glass doors that lead to a covered lanai and pool area with new pool pump system. The entire first level is tiled. All bedrooms are on the second level and have hardwood flooring. The master bedroom has a huge walk-in closet, with an ensuite master bath. This master suite has a private balcony off the bedroom which offers a secluded and peaceful sanctuary. The fenced in yard has a tropical pool design with plenty of space to entertain and enjoy quality family time. Enjoy the central Palm Harbor location with easy access shopping, the beaches, restaurants, state parks and the outstanding schools of the area. Palm Harbor is one of Pinellas County's best kept secrets and places to live. Small, Quaint Quiet Neighborhood. Welcome Home. No HOA or CDD fees.  Welcome home. Seller Motivated - Seller willing to contribute closing costs assistance with acceptable offer.
